APPS:
wm:		bspwm
bar:		polybar
hotkey:		sxhkd
bg:		feh
term:		alacritty
comp:		picom
menu:		rofi
notif:		dunst
prtsc:		scrot
editor:		vim
volume:		pamixer(PULSEAUDIO NEEDED!)
passwd_store:	pass
mail:		neomutt(mutt-wizard)
lock:		physlock
automount:	udiskie

GTK theme:	Nordic
Cursor theme:	Adwaita

Fonts:
Source Code Pro:	terminal
Roboto:			polybar text
Symbols Nerd Font:	polybar icons

App shortcuts:
Alt + K:	KeePassXC
Alt + F:	Firefox
Alt + D:	Discord
Alt + T:	Microsoft Teams
Alt + S:	Spotify
Alt + M:	Mail custom script(neomutt + mbsync)

Other shortcuts:
Alt + plus: 	Increase window gap
Alt + minus: 	Decrease window gap
Alt + R:	Rotate windows

IMPORTANT:
"sudo poweroff" and "sudo reboot" commands need to be allowed to execute without a password for those functions to work from the bar.
The xinitrc sets the keyboard layout to Hungarian.
LaTeX-Suite plugin for vim recommended.
